dataset_description.json.Name: Brainstem fMRI signaling of surprise across different types of deviant stimuli
EthicsApprovals: French national ethics committee (Comit√© de Protection des Personnes Ile de France 3, approval #2018-A03195-50)

README:
This dataset includes anatomical and functional images of 24 participants that have performed the local-global task. Functional images are:
- 4 runs partial-brain functional echo planar images (EPI) images centered on the brainstem
- 2 volumes with opposite phase encoding directions: anterior to posterior direction (AP) and the other direction (PA) Anatomical images are:
- 2 partial-brain Turbo Spin Echo (TSE)
- 1 whole-brain structural T1 image with an MPRAGE sequence Behavioural, physiological, and pupil data can be found on OSF at https://osf.io/td5kp/ .
